{"type":"message","id":"558044a0","parentId":"d3beddae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:52:06.057Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 20:52 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下主题的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新趋势\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成技术趋势\n4. IT运维服务行业发展\n\n请为每个主题整理1-2条关键信息，最终输出3-5条对道简网络最有价值的行业动态。要求简洁，直接给出结果。"}],"timestamp":1774011126056}}
{"type":"message","id":"5cf7a93d","parentId":"558044a0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:52:37.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索4个主题的最新动态（2026年3月），并整理出对道简网络最有价值的3-5条行业动态。\n\n我需要搜索：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新趋势\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成技术趋势\n4. IT运维服务行业发展\n\n让我使用web-search skill来搜索这些主题。","thinkingSignature":"7dcc2c79af36c9c33accd75c7c185a506a2bf7e2210b88d7ed034b71d8f32be3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k4fsz00i02nz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.agents/skills/web-search && cat SKILL.md | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108,"output":118,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30603,"totalTokens":30829,"cost":{"input":0.0000324,"output":0.0001416,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036723599999999995,"total":0.0038463599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774011126057}}
{"type":"message","id":"043be948","parentId":"5cf7a93d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:52:37.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k4fsz00i02nz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: web-search\ndescription: \"Web search and content extraction with Tavily and Exa via inference.sh CLI. Apps: Tavily Search, Tavily Extract, Exa Search, Exa Answer, Exa Extract. Capabilities: AI-powered search, content extraction, direct answers, research. Use for: research, RAG pipelines, fact-checking, content aggregation, agents. Triggers: web search, tavily, exa, search api, content extraction, research, internet search, ai search, search assistant, web scraping, rag, perplexity alternative\"\nallowed-tools: Bash(infsh *)\n---\n\n# Web Search & Extraction\n\nSearch the web and extract content via [inference.sh](https://inference.sh) CLI.\n\n![Web Search & Extraction](https://cloud.inference.sh/app/files/u/4mg21r6ta37mpaz6ktzwtt8krr/01kgndqjxd780zm2j3rmada6y8.jpeg)\n\n## Quick Start\n\n> Requires inference.sh CLI (`infsh`). Get installation instructions: `npx skills add inference-sh/skills@agent-tools`\n\n```bash\ninfsh login\n\n# Search the web\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\"query\": \"latest AI developments 2024\"}'\n```\n\n\n## Available Apps\n\n### Tavily\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search Assistant | `tavily/search-assistant` | AI-powered search with answers |\n| Extract | `tavily/extract` | Extract content from URLs |\n\n### Exa\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search | `exa/search` | Smart web search with AI |\n| Answer | `exa/answer` | Direct factual answers |\n| Extract | `exa/extract` | Extract and analyze web content |\n\n## Examples\n\n### Tavily Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\n  \"query\": \"What are the best practices for building AI agents?\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns AI-generated answers with sources and images.\n\n### Tavily Extract\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/extract --input '{\n  \"urls\": [\"https://example.com/article1\", \"https://example.com/article2\"]\n}'\n```\n\nExtracts clean text and images from multiple URLs.\n\n### Exa Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/search --input '{\n  \"query\": \"machine learning frameworks comparison\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns highly relevant links with context.\n\n### Exa Answer\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/answer --input '{\n  \"question\": \"What is the population of Tokyo?\"\n}'\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"---\nname: web-search\ndescription: \"Web search and content extraction with Tavily and Exa via inference.sh CLI. Apps: Tavily Search, Tavily Extract, Exa Search, Exa Answer, Exa Extract. Capabilities: AI-powered search, content extraction, direct answers, research. Use for: research, RAG pipelines, fact-checking, content aggregation, agents. Triggers: web search, tavily, exa, search api, content extraction, research, internet search, ai search, search assistant, web scraping, rag, perplexity alternative\"\nallowed-tools: Bash(infsh *)\n---\n\n# Web Search & Extraction\n\nSearch the web and extract content via [inference.sh](https://inference.sh) CLI.\n\n![Web Search & Extraction](https://cloud.inference.sh/app/files/u/4mg21r6ta37mpaz6ktzwtt8krr/01kgndqjxd780zm2j3rmada6y8.jpeg)\n\n## Quick Start\n\n> Requires inference.sh CLI (`infsh`). Get installation instructions: `npx skills add inference-sh/skills@agent-tools`\n\n```bash\ninfsh login\n\n# Search the web\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\"query\": \"latest AI developments 2024\"}'\n```\n\n\n## Available Apps\n\n### Tavily\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search Assistant | `tavily/search-assistant` | AI-powered search with answers |\n| Extract | `tavily/extract` | Extract content from URLs |\n\n### Exa\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search | `exa/search` | Smart web search with AI |\n| Answer | `exa/answer` | Direct factual answers |\n| Extract | `exa/extract` | Extract and analyze web content |\n\n## Examples\n\n### Tavily Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\n  \"query\": \"What are the best practices for building AI agents?\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns AI-generated answers with sources and images.\n\n### Tavily Extract\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/extract --input '{\n  \"urls\": [\"https://example.com/article1\", \"https://example.com/article2\"]\n}'\n```\n\nExtracts clean text and images from multiple URLs.\n\n### Exa Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/search --input '{\n  \"query\": \"machine learning frameworks comparison\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns highly relevant links with context.\n\n### Exa Answer\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/answer --input '{\n  \"question\": \"What is the population of Tokyo?\"\n}'\n```","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774011157233}}
